sentences: Torun Eriksen (born 8 January 1977 in Lunde, Telemark) is a Norwegian jazz singer, whose musical talents first came to prominence as a music student at high school in Norway.
After moving to Oslo in 1997, she enrolled at the Norwegian Institute for Stage and Studio.
